Text: FREE Compensation Survey Results Available for Financial Professionalsyou know how your salary and benefits rate The results of the Association for Financial Professionals AFP th Annual Compensation Survey are now in and we have created a special summary report yours FREE for the asking Data for this special report was compiled from surveys submitted by members of AFP and The Financial Executives Networking Group FENG an AFP sponsored networking and exchange organization To receive your free copy email AFP Managing Director of Membership Dave Lewis at mailtodslAFPonlineorg The survey results come in printed form so be sure to indicate your preferred mailing address and title AFP is a community of more than professionals representing a broad spectrum of financial disciplines To learn more about AFP and how you can become a member click on With over pages and interactive finance communities is the ultimate resource for information news and tools for the treasury and finance professional Hope to hear from you soon Jim Kaitz President CEO Association for Financial Professionals This message is brought to you as a registered user or subscriber to Economistcom If you wish to discontinue receiving third party messages simply reply to this email with the word UNSUBSCRIBE in the subject line Please be sure to use reply rather than composing a new message so that we may properly handle your request
